{#
/**
 * @file
 * Default theme implementation to display a node of type 'Petition'.
 * --------------
 * @author christopherj.allen@bia.gov
 * --------------
 * The content type displays different fields based on "Template to Use" field
 *    (Options: 1978, 1994, 2015)
